Amazon EBS(Elastic Bloc Store )

Amazon EBS is a block-level storage serviec used mainly with ec2 instances to store data like:
i)Operating system ii)Aplication files iii)DAtabases  iv)logs


key Points:
Persistent storage -> data remains even if ec2 stops
works like a virtual hard disk
Attached to Ec2 instances 
Automatically replicated within an Availability Zone 


Common EBS Volume Types
gp3/gp2 General purpose(most used)
io1/io2 high performance databsases
st1- Throughput optimized (big data)
sc1 cold storage(low cost)


